38:18.920 --> 38:19.967
[door closes]

38:20.640 --> 38:23.689
<i>II</i>

38:27.520 --> 38:28.567
[tires screech]

38:29.520 --> 38:31.443
Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa!

38:33.680 --> 38:36.524
One thing I hate... waiting.

38:36.840 --> 38:40.526
Cable guy, UPS, mailman, you.

38:40.600 --> 38:42.523
I can't just go to
the Tooth Fairy and get him

38:42.600 --> 38:44.125
to tell me all the bad things
he's ever done.

38:44.200 --> 38:45.406
It doesn't work like that.

38:45.800 --> 38:46.847
One or two would do.

38:47.120 --> 38:48.770
I have something
that might interest you, though.

38:49.920 --> 38:50.967
The Asians?

38:51.400 --> 38:55.371
Getting a huge shipment
of blow coming in any day.

38:55.440 --> 38:56.601
[tires screech]

38:57.240 --> 38:59.129
- God!
- I don't give a rat's ass

38:59.240 --> 39:00.480
about the Asians.

39:00.560 --> 39:02.050
I want that fat Polak.

39:04.920 --> 39:06.649
Ahab, remember?
Huh?

39:07.040 --> 39:10.726
- White whale, remember?
- [grunts]

39:15.520 --> 39:16.806
Get out of my car.

39:35.000 --> 39:36.365
[Tommy] Hey, buddy. How's it going?

39:36.480 --> 39:39.006
Why don't you head upstairs,
get ready for bed, yeah?

39:39.080 --> 39:40.206
I'll be up in a minute.

39:47.760 --> 39:49.967
- You're late.
- You don't discipline the boy?

39:50.040 --> 39:51.883
What?
What do you mean?

39:53.200 --> 39:55.009
You might want to teach him
some rules.

39:55.120 --> 39:56.645
Does things without asking.

39:57.400 --> 40:00.006
Free thinker, like his mother.

40:00.680 --> 40:03.331
Never say anything about my wife.

40:12.960 --> 40:14.962
Hey, Teej, you left
your math book on the--

40:16.040 --> 40:17.610
What's that?

40:18.920 --> 40:20.410
Hey, what is that?

40:21.160 --> 40:22.764
Hey.

40:28.760 --> 40:30.125
Where'd you get those bruises?

40:33.960 --> 40:36.804
It's really important you tell me
where you got those bruises.

40:38.480 --> 40:40.130
Did that happen today?

40:47.040 --> 40:48.087
Okay, get in bed.

40:49.320 --> 40:52.642
Do your homework.
Do not leave this room.

40:55.880 --> 40:56.927
[door closes]

40:59.360 --> 41:00.441
You son of a bitch.

41:01.680 --> 41:02.727
You hit my kid?

41:03.200 --> 41:07.125
Suppose I did.
What would you do about it?

41:09.600 --> 41:11.489
You are not doing that to him,
too, you mother--

41:11.560 --> 41:12.607
[grunting]

41:13.400 --> 41:16.609
<i>II</i>

41:24.200 --> 41:25.247
[gun cocks]

41:27.320 --> 41:28.890
I'd blow your brains out,

41:29.480 --> 41:31.847
but this is a $30,000 Persian rug.

41:43.720 --> 41:45.085
[Tommy]
We're done with him!

41:45.320 --> 41:47.721
I don't want anything to do
with that scum-sucking

41:47.960 --> 41:51.487
son of a bitch
or his goddamn dirty money!

41:51.560 --> 41:53.801
I don't care if we don't do
the restaurant, all right?!

41:53.880 --> 41:57.521
We are not doing business
with my father!

41:58.040 --> 42:01.010
Okay. I hear you.

42:05.520 --> 42:07.010
Something wrong?

42:10.400 --> 42:11.686
Nope.
[chuckles lightly]

42:12.960 --> 42:14.007
All good.

